{"ts":"2026-07-14T19:04:33.488Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-nmzx"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-562: pm init rejects --id-prefix/--prefix flag though id prefix is only positional"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"GH-562: the workspace id prefix is configured by the field literally named id_prefix, so agents naturally try 'pm init --id-prefix opstest' and hit Unknown option (exit 2). Every other init setup value is flag-based (--author, --preset, ...), making the positional-only prefix the odd one out. Fix = add --id-prefix (and optionally --prefix) as a flag alias; wire through the full new-flag checklist. Related: pm-kl19 owns RENAMING an existing prefix (GH-548); this item is creation-time input ergonomics only. pm-3mna's init SDK slice will carry the same option surface — land this before or with that slice to avoid contract churn."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","cli","github-issue","init"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-14T19:04:33.488Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-14T19:04:33.488Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":60},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"pm init accepts --id-prefix <value> as an alias for the positional prefix argument (positional form stays supported); conflicting positional + flag values fail fast with a clear message; help text, completion (bash+zsh+fish), contracts (cli-contracts.ts flag contracts + MCP schema), and docs updated per the new-flag wiring checklist; regression spec covers flag form, positional form, and the conflict case"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-3mna","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-14T19:04:33.488Z"},{"id":"pm-kl19","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-14T19:04:33.488Z"}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"bb6dfd04415cc8d202da4f7c2573108dc2ad4103c9884e8211b10f9bf228448c","message":""}
